Metropolitan Consolidated Industries Incsaid it will make a tender offer for all or any of theoutstanding shares of common stock of Metex Corp &lt;MTX> notcurrently held by or under option to Metropolitan for 7.75 dlrsper share.    The company said the offer will be subject ot securingsatisfactory financing.    Metropolitan currently owns about 25.7 pct of Metex commonand holds options to purchase about an additional 16 pct ofMetex common stock.       Metropolitan said the offer will be made no later thanOctober 27. Reuter&#3;